  "detailed_description": "Dolphin Swim<br>A simple experience in seeing how long you can last navigating a zig zag path.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047720/extras/4c51bfe17e9a29ffcab293b073db1ac0.avif?t=1724953734\" width=64 height=64 /></span><br>It's all about FOCUS!<br>Whether you want to be a musician, pro gamer, or even a developer and more!<br>You're going to need a lot of focus!<br><br>Dolphin Swim aligns your brain's focus with a creative zigzag game!<br>Playing Dolphin Swim every morning can get your brain ready to reach your dreams!<br>Your score is your brain's focus strength for the day. A strength above 100 isn't necessary.<br>Dolphin Swim can even be a stress test for some people.<br><br>~Work your way up to a score of 100 everyday!~<br><br>Some Focus examples<br>Focus Speed 1: Attentive - 100 focus<br><br>Focus Speed 2<br>House Chores 20 - 25 focus<br>Homework 35 - 50 focus<br>Out of Bed 10 - 15 focus<br>Your Dreams 90 - 100 focus<br><br>Focus Speed 3<br>Reaction - 3 focus<br>Precision Timing Storage - 6 focus<br>Technique Discovery - 10 focus<br><br>Events to earn new achievements come and go but return eventually at random.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047720/extras/84b83f5f85df3e1fe77cd1c972b0eefd.avif?t=1724953734\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047720/extras/50dad1282115438c4f729548751b213f.avif?t=1724953734\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047720/extras/69719bd439a976aa18edc7bdb3a3e0cc.avif?t=1724953734\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047720/extras/17def9884ac9c420c25565e5347370b0.avif?t=1724953734\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047720/extras/d3cb2b1548813cac4c0c4fc1ebcf7b3a.avif?t=1724953734\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047720/extras/1085811966b7fce86e912e2edcd5f81f.avif?t=1724953734\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047720/extras/a28ec3a7022cdc2adc1c512cfdb009f6.avif?t=1724953734\" width=64 height=64 /></span><br>Eventually you can earn all of the achievements!<br>Events may contain challenge mode achievements that are a little harder to earn than others!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047720/extras/376e768fb4e1e621852313029ba75d98.avif?t=1724953734\" width=64 height=64 /></span>>>><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047720/extras/fa7888399733f92b48020cd628ad3d94.avif?t=1724953734\" width=64 height=64 /></span><br><br>~You can play Dolphin Swim with only a keyboard if you like, mouse, or both!~<br>Mouse<br>Left Click: Everything<br><br>Keyboard<br>D, S, Spacebar: Swim<br>Enter: Start, Restart<br>Q: Quality Toggle<br>W: Focus Speed<br>E: Sound Mute<br>R: Game Mode<br>T: Trophy (Extended Mode)<br>Y: Event (Extended Mode)<br>M: Music Mute<br>P: Pause (Original Mode)<br>B: Background Animation<br>U: Mirror Effect<br>I: Many Textures<br>O: Background Toggle<br>H: Hide/Show Focus Meter<br>Esc: Close<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047720/extras/cd211164a9ba3292268d315850c2732b.avif?t=1724953734\" width=128 height=64 /></span><br>~Go ahead. Give it a try!~",
  "about_the_game": "Dolphin Swim<br>A simple experience in seeing how long you can last navigating a zig zag path.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047720/extras/4c51bfe17e9a29ffcab293b073db1ac0.avif?t=1724953734\" width=64 height=64 /></span><br>It's all about FOCUS!<br>Whether you want to be a musician, pro gamer, or even a developer and more!<br>You're going to need a lot of focus!<br><br>Dolphin Swim aligns your brain's focus with a creative zigzag game!<br>Playing Dolphin Swim every morning can get your brain ready to reach your dreams!<br>Your score is your brain's focus strength for the day. A strength above 100 isn't necessary.<br>Dolphin Swim can even be a stress test for some people.<br><br>~Work your way up to a score of 100 everyday!~<br><br>Some Focus examples<br>Focus Speed 1: Attentive - 100 focus<br><br>Focus Speed 2<br>House Chores 20 - 25 focus<br>Homework 35 - 50 focus<br>Out of Bed 10 - 15 focus<br>Your Dreams 90 - 100 focus<br><br>Focus Speed 3<br>Reaction - 3 focus<br>Precision Timing Storage - 6 focus<br>Technique Discovery - 10 focus<br><br>Events to earn new achievements come and go but return eventually at random.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047720/extras/84b83f5f85df3e1fe77cd1c972b0eefd.avif?t=1724953734\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047720/extras/50dad1282115438c4f729548751b213f.avif?t=1724953734\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047720/extras/69719bd439a976aa18edc7bdb3a3e0cc.avif?t=1724953734\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstati